Boom 💥 Malcom X Warned us about the White Liberal elite establishment that pretends to be for black people while implementing policies that have destroyed the black family & black society by extension. 

Notice that Malcom X points out the fact that everything the left does is for their own political benefit & not to benefit the blacks they purport to be for. 

Sadly so many black people have been blinded into believing the white liberal complex is for them & have voted to keep them in power 

Notice what he says about the so called “black leaders”
 They are puppets. 

Hollywood & entertainment industry run by the white liberal elite establishment controls what black entertainers succeed which ones don’t. 

The only black  celebrities that are given a platform are those that parrot the  talking points the elite liberal establishment wants put out to the black community. Talking points that keep blacks seeing themselves as victims & present the Democrat party as the savior. 

Those celebs that don’t toe the line are quickly destroyed. Look what they did to Kanye when he started to color outside the lines. 

They threw him into a mental institution & intimidated him into silence about his political & religious beliefs. 

The elite liberal establishment has always propped up entertainers to represent black leaders. They took the black father out of the home, put him into the prison system, & then propped up celebrities, rappers & athletes THEY CONTROL to be “leaders” of the society. 
They taught them to reject Real leaders & black American heroes like Dr. Ben Carson a neurosurgeon but embrace athletes & rappers. 

Malcom X spoke of these things all the time & it’s sad to see decades later, some still don’t see through the tactics & deceit of the elite liberal establishment 

Share #malcomx

Had the great honor of speaking at a Frederick Douglas Foundation event with other black Americans who standing up against #criticalracetheory or what I like to call the Black Demoralization project. 

Had Frederick Douglas been taught under #CRT, as a child of a slave, he never would have achieved any of what he was able to accomplish. He became one of the wealthiest men in America when systemic racism actually existed. But in 2021, the left pays rich black athletes & entertainers to teach other black people that they are helpless & oppressed. It’s evil & is a mentality that is manifesting poverty & defeat among many blacks. 
Reject it!
